name: The Good Boys @ Tai Seng

reviews.text: This outlet is a great choice for those seeking nutritious and delicious meals. Their healthy bowls are well-balanced, packed with fresh ingredients, and thoughtfully crafted for both taste and nutrition. The variety of options ensures there is something for everyone, making it a perfect spot for a guilt-free yet satisfying meal. Highly recommended for health-conscious diners!
Review is for the coffee only. Average coffee. Milky and not as strong. Perhaps should add 1 more shot. Nonetheless quiet cafe, reasonable price and friendly service.
